[{"id":916682,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1673261684","description":"","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/916682","replies":216,"created_ts":1676533775,"created":"15:49:35","title":"看头条说俄亥俄留学生看到国内热搜才知道出事是真的吗","author":"Huelse","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Huelse","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6310/dfed/365483_mini.png?m=1635240198"},{"id":916559,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","description":"<p>如果这个人是陌生人呢？</p>\n<p>如果这个人是我的好朋友呢？</p>\n<p>如果我发现我的好朋友正在网上学习某某老师的课程，但是我去看这个老师的课程发现非常庸俗，我应该告诉我的朋友吗？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/916559","replies":155,"created_ts":1676515185,"created":"10:39:45","title":"人应该鄙视他人的庸俗吗？","author":"sdjl","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/sdjl","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/be6a/d876/5055_mini.png?m=1477473640"},{"id":916597,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1673261684","description":"<h2>一、事情开始</h2>\n<p>几天前七牛云发短信提醒我该充钱了，我也没有太多理会；周末又给我发了一条提醒消息，限时余额还有 2r..</p>\n<p><img alt=\"image\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/13310916-04f4f49777197a03.image?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\"/></p>\n<p>周末忙完后，登录了七牛云后台打算充值一下，看了一下几个空间的占用情况，其中一个用于开源项目的空间占用的存储量高的有点异常！ 199.93GB ，我想了一下：演示环境中都是测试数据在使用，不会存在这么大量的内容使用。那就只有一种可能，被人恶搞或者被人当做正式环境使用！</p>\n<p><img alt=\"image\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/13310916-a6cdd9bbc0eed80b.image?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\"/></p>\n<p>查看了一下统计分析，根据时间筛选了一下发现，22 年 8 月有异常，存储量飙升！</p>\n<p><img alt=\"image\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/13310916-ac35615e1fcf17c5.image?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\"/></p>\n<h2>二、开始排查</h2>\n<p>知道大概的异常时间后，我直接进入开源版项目的数据库，开始查表；（ ps：由于该项目为开源表单系统，表单存在一张表里面）于是，直接倒序查询所有时间段内，表单为单位，统计收集的数据条数。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"image\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/13310916-ddffd275be376250.image?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\"/></p>\n<p>添加图片注释，不超过 140 字（可选）</p>\n<p>好家伙，不查不知道，一查下一跳！当成正式环境使用的人还不少....随机查了几个账号下收集的内容；截图如下</p>\n<p><img alt=\"image\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/13310916-ae0fdd0bf0d55e53.image?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\"/></p>\n<p>这个是 ts 打人事件后的一个调研</p>\n<p><img alt=\"image\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/13310916-7e204e6bac131ed3.image?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\"/></p>\n<p>这个是哪位大哥做的数据收集，全是大附件！！！</p>\n<p><img alt=\"image\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/13310916-b0cdcd940133e4b6.image?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\"/></p>\n<p>这位直接暴露了学生的身份证号.....</p>\n<p>还有很多收集的内容不一一列举了。</p>\n<h2>三、如何处理</h2>\n<p>为了避免再出现这样的情况，设置了一个数据库定时任务，定时清理表单数据，如果有伙伴拿它当 saas 使用的话，那小心数据没了....</p>\n<p><img alt=\"image\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/13310916-dbe75440cb62bc29.image?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\"/></p>\n<p><img alt=\"image\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/13310916-b245c8f568015478.image?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\"/></p>\n<p>😅 没有办法大兄弟，存储还是有点小贵的</p>\n<h2>四、建议</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://gitee.com/TDuckApp/tduck-platform\" rel=\"nofollow\">填鸭表单 — 开源表单系统</a> 是一款开源表单系统，可以自行部署在自己的服务器上做数据收集，部署文档也有整理公开，<a href=\"http://doc.tduckcloud.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">填鸭表单帮助中心</a> 如有需求，请自行部署在使用🙏🏻（给跪了！</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/916597","replies":137,"created_ts":1676518413,"created":"11:33:33","title":"开源项目的体验环境被人当成 saas 在用....","author":"tduck","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/tduck","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9ebec02930e0f0401709a217125b6393?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":916524,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","description":"<p>由于种种原因，已经很久没坐地铁了，前几天第一次坐地铁（广州），竟然还是要戴口罩。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/916524","replies":129,"created_ts":1676510157,"created":"09:15:57","title":"已经放开这么久了，为什么地铁还是要戴口罩？","author":"JasonLaw","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/JasonLaw","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/4fdf59ece7cd78f432ec513634889579?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":916502,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","description":"<p>曾经我以为分手没什么大不了，直到落在我身上，我才知道有多么痛！\n深夜沸点，毕竟在深圳，一个朋友都没有。</p>\n<p>前提：\n1.家里农村，没啥钱，20 年毕业来深圳工作，身无分文，到此时大概工作了 2 年半多\n2.我以为我俩会结婚\n3.我提了几次分手，要复合需要给钱，第一次多少，第二次成倍等等，总共大概 10w 。\n4.双方约定谁出轨，谁要把“我给的钱”还给对方\n5.第一次谈恋爱</p>\n<p>1.矛盾产生-纪念日的礼物\n恋爱纪念日，2 月 6 号，没有提前准备礼物，他说要黄金，故转了 3990(10 克黄金)，当天她微信给我转了 520 。2 月 7 号，问我是不是没有提前准备礼物，我就敷衍说提前看了，问我要浏览器历史记录，我骗她 safari 会自动清理记录，机智的她识破了我的骗局，我也忘记了我说了啥让她说出：“那我就分手后，在找个，不用给你钱”，这句话顿时将我炸裂，我再次提出了分手</p>\n<p>2.雪上加霜-情人节前的礼物\n由于一个在龙华、一个在宝安，在情人节前的周五她收到 1000+的 CT 化妆品，我在周六开好了房（她就在床上会温柔，我想在床上征服它，让她认识到这句话对我的伤害，并保证以后不再说这种话），然后以“去拿电磁炉的理由去找她”。我到了后，她刚好下班，我在她家门口，微信让她带饭，回复“为什么给你带”。此时我就有点死心了。后面他把电磁炉给了我，并且进屋拿电磁炉还把门挡住，此时我彻底死心。下楼时没想到他给的袋子不结实，电磁炉掉地上碎了，瞬间感觉心冷。到楼底查看碎的怎么样，发现她把化妆品也放进去了，微信问化妆品不要？回：不要。我将这俩丢进了垃 圾 桶，然后退款了情人节的花，并删除微信</p>\n<p>3.移除痕迹-结束即是新的开始\n就在刚刚，打完篮球地铁回来，以“还钱”为理由（说实话有点想复合，但想到那句话我真的过去），让她把我纪念日转的 3990 还给我，她说我在纪念日礼物骗她，敷衍她，说我是“贱人”，“狗”等等，当然我也开启了喷粪模式。随后她把我拉黑，于此我彻底死心，每个软件都发消息，她一一将我删掉（我确实舍不得删掉）</p>\n<p>发完这个沸点，感觉内心好多了，已经在重新开始的路上了，虽然分手确实痛。现在我唯一耿耿于怀的是 10w 我能否要回来，该以什么方式要回来，能要回来多少。在今天的聊天中我以“你要有良心就还给我”为要挟，但她说她没良心，我就卡壳了，感觉无从下手。各位 JY 有什么好方法。说实话在事件 [ 2.雪上加霜-情人节前的礼物] 之后我是没打算要钱的（可能我还没到用钱的阶段，感觉没啥），但在 [ 3.移除痕迹-结束即是新的开始] 之后，我想把属于我自己的“血汗钱”拿回来</p>\n<p>或许有人喷我，特别设置了投票环节</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/916502","replies":123,"created_ts":1676480111,"created":"00:55:11","title":"曾经我以为分手没什么大不了，直到落在我身上，我才知道有多么痛！","author":"Azzsanjin","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Azzsanjin","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/55a2603313276f4ab43460657f98c612?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":916585,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","description":"昨日的热搜：揭开北京二手房成交率提升的真相<br />今日的热搜：疫情三年，房价涨回来只用了一周<br /><br />百度搜索里排第一个，现在还能看到。<br /><br />一触即发，真是不容易啊","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/916585","replies":115,"created_ts":1676517633,"created":"11:20:33","title":"房价又开始了","author":"q474818917","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/q474818917","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/e628155cbe8ac15e9c48b87a0591ee2c?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":916516,"node":"Windows","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/windows","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_mini.png?m=1670319927","description":"<p>不管是热门的、冷门的，还是常用的、偶尔用的，只要实用好用的。</p>\n<p>抛砖引玉：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Wisereminder: 免费的事件提醒工具，可以用作每日的工作提醒。</li>\n<li>Motrix: 一款全能的下载工具。支持下载 HTTP 、FTP 、BT 、磁力链接等资源。</li>\n<li>洛雪音乐: 一个聚合音乐软件。</li>\n<li>Wireshark: 一个网络包分析工具。</li>\n<li>Prince: Convert HTML to PDF with CSS ，结合 Markdown Preview Enhanced 可以将 md 文件转成带目录的 pdf 文件，非常方便。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>等等等等……还有什么使用小工具，请大家多多分享。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/916516","replies":95,"created_ts":1676508602,"created":"08:50:02","title":"Windows 上有哪些实用的小工具？","author":"klo424","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/klo424","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/13d9/41b7/59091_mini.png?m=1646267791"},{"id":916640,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","description":"预算：2w 左右<br /><br />需求：外观炫酷，配置高(这个我详细问了需求是啥，但回复就是要配置高，只能根据预算凑了)<br /><br />我给个配置方案如下：<br /><br />CPU+主板：i5-13600kf,ROG Z790-A 吹雪 WIFI D4,合计 4900<br />显卡：铭瑄 4070ti ，合计 6799<br />固态：致态 7100 系列 2TB ，合计 1200<br />内存：金百达 刃系列 3600 频率，RGB 灯条 16Gx2 ，合计 719<br />电源：振华额定 850W ，合计 1099<br />机箱：联力包豪斯 evo 纯白+三代积木风扇*6 ，合计 2199<br />散热：利民风冷 fc140,合计 350<br /><br />网上搜了一圈，听说 13 代 U 跟 DDR4 内存不兼容？ 在想主板要不要上 D5 的，这样内存条就可以选用 DDR5 的来兼容了？大伙有啥建议吗","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/916640","replies":78,"created_ts":1676526763,"created":"13:52:43","title":"日经贴，亲戚让帮忙组装台式机，大伙看看我的方案如何","author":"fatyoung","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/fatyoung","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f4b019dbc49ce159e281baa44bc9f912?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":916534,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1673261684","description":"<p><a href=\"https://github.com/zloirock/core-js/blob/master/docs/2023-02-14-so-whats-next.md\" rel=\"nofollow\">core-js 的作者在人生低谷期总结了自己的遭遇</a>，其中提到开发者的仇恨令人悲哀，而这个似乎是很普遍的现象。</p>\n<p>同行相轻无可厚非，但为什么会对一个与自己利益毫无相关的同行充满恶意，甚至付出诸如诋毁、恶言相向等仇恨的行为呢？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/916534","replies":71,"created_ts":1676511425,"created":"09:37:05","title":"仇恨开源作者的开发者群体是什么心理？","author":"Micropaper","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Micropaper","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f495/5f4d/567068_mini.png?m=1674874375"},{"id":916683,"node":"生活","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/life","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785","description":"<p>各位周末双休都是怎么过的，在出租屋打游戏是在无聊，想找点事做</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/916683","replies":70,"created_ts":1676533793,"created":"15:49:53","title":"有尝试在周末双休时跑外卖的吗？","author":"xiaohusky","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/xiaohusky","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/38fdcf96777036511be2ca942f81eb73?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":916651,"node":"分享发现","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/share","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_mini.png?m=1650127281","description":"<p><img alt=\"image.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/29458389/1676527755339-da81d9a4-0065-4caa-b5a4-999c0b170a86.png#averageHue=%239ba5bb&amp;clientId=udc98f5fd-3547-4&amp;from=paste&amp;height=824&amp;id=ue57ba4ef&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=1043&amp;originWidth=945&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=1.100000023841858&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=1315519&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=ucd2dd7d7-435f-4407-817d-da5b5478446&amp;title=&amp;width=747\"/>\n<img alt=\"image.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/29458389/1676527822591-137ba21d-c38b-4c1d-8934-5eb2d8a921d7.png#averageHue=%234f6a42&amp;clientId=udc98f5fd-3547-4&amp;from=paste&amp;height=506&amp;id=ucdbeb50d&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=556&amp;originWidth=720&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=1.100000023841858&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=532491&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=u18b5215e-2a5e-4a01-b5f7-9ae76c51793&amp;title=&amp;width=655\"/></p>\n<p>部分朋友说：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>医保分为基础 VIP 版 和 SVIP 版...</li>\n<li>挺好的，只是针对一部分人....</li>\n<li>不想交社保了，能给我折现吗？</li>\n<li>这条消息不利于群众的团结，建议删除...</li>\n<li>人民有医保，名族有希望。支持，顶，赞。</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>我就想知道你们怎么看？</strong></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/916651","replies":60,"created_ts":1676528320,"created":"14:18:40","title":"医保年限又延长咯，缴到 20-25 年方可享受？","author":"freepoint","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/freepoint","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/67c7b69d75806df289428ef5e7ec3b1e?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":916507,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1673261684","description":"<p>上个帖子发帖吐槽了一下树莓派的卡顿问题，有个老哥留言说不如趁现在高价把树莓派卖了，买个 NUC 性能会高很多，功耗没高几瓦。</p>\n<p>说实话很心动，但是该老哥推荐的 n5105 后来查证社区反应有很多问题，而且还都是比较大的问题，不太能接受。</p>\n<p>平时不关注小主机市场，不知道有没有老哥熟悉具体型号，英特尔 J4125 到 N5105 这条产品线是唯一选择？今年有什么好产品吗？</p>\n<p>（注：需求就是想家里起一台类似云主机的服务，需要 7*24 执行一些轻型计算 /网络任务。其实说实话现在树莓派的性能是能 carry 的，但是既然能增加性能谁又会不愿意呢。。。）</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/916507","replies":53,"created_ts":1676491455,"created":"04:04:15","title":"2023 年小主机有什么不错的具体型号推荐吗？","author":"LeeReamond","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/LeeReamond","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f481/5f03/469082_mini.png?m=1657573522"},{"id":916726,"node":"Java","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/java","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/03af/dbd6/63_mini.png?m=1644490200","description":"如果没使用 IDEA 请忽略这个问题<br /><br />Xms 是否额外配置了呢？<br /><br />我个人的配置是-Xms6G -Xmx6G","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/916726","replies":45,"created_ts":1676540224,"created":"17:37:04","title":"各位 Javaer 给 IDEA 分配多大内存？","author":"hex2en","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/hex2en","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0cb9ab771879c72cecb38a6947443d2a?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":916679,"node":"Linux","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/linux","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6512/bd43/11_mini.png?m=1651565926","description":"<p>如题, 谢谢~</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/916679","replies":45,"created_ts":1676533525,"created":"15:45:25","title":"要求在 Linux 和 Windows 系统下都可以用的 PC 软件, 现在一般使用什么语言和平台开发?","author":"JimmyChan1506","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/JimmyChan1506","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f121a7434fce108c25344d55ef36cecb?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":916645,"node":"区块链","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/blockchain","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/5d61/6dd3/1017_mini.png?m=1641688488","description":"有想加群的， 留下微信号， 我拉人。","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/916645","replies":45,"created_ts":1676527356,"created":"14:02:36","title":"个人力量是在是太小， 我建了一个群， 一起研究项目， 撸空投。","author":"llentskynet2","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/llentskynet2","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/4ad2751712390635fdb4286d3077d279?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":916604,"node":"iPhone","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/iphone","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_mini.png?m=1630643991","description":"<p>我媳妇用的<strong>11 Pro Max</strong> <strong>重度</strong>用户，电池健康 <strong>79%</strong> </p>\n<p>我用的<strong>Xs Max</strong> <strong>轻度</strong>用户 电池健康 <strong>80%</strong> </p>\n<p>换<strong>2</strong>块电池 价格：<strong>1k</strong></p>\n<p>纠结的点：是以后过 1 年直接买新款，还是换个电池再战<strong>3 年</strong>，因为手机目前使用功能都正常，就是电池不太行，有时候电量低会<strong>降频杀后台</strong>，换了之后可能使用<strong>体验会提升</strong>一些。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/916604","replies":45,"created_ts":1676518968,"created":"11:42:48","title":"iPhone 手机电池该不该换，有点纠结","author":"itcong","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/itcong","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/245f/ff13/215214_mini.png?m=1641276783"},{"id":916563,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","description":"目前：<br />还是差不多 16 年自己搞的电脑<br />6700K+Z170 板子<br />显卡 1070<br /><br />需求：<br />平时喜欢多开网游，cpu 瓶颈了<br />希望大家推荐下板 U ，<br /><br />预算:<br />预算 2000 内，性价比，量能十足的话 3000 也可<br /><br />另外问下，显卡的接口是通用的哈？<br />（板子话需要 M2 接口，四个内存插口，目前应该都有把）","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/916563","replies":44,"created_ts":1676515858,"created":"10:50:58","title":"PC 升级，大家推荐下板 U","author":"SWALLOWW","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/SWALLOWW","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/95ec/01ce/496681_mini.png?m=1676515845"}]